dictionary.description: Had Zellha not been stopped by a disciple and her invasion of the Bariura Empire proceeded as planned, she might have succeeded in seizing the magical secrets of the dark magician who deceived her and in making them her own. In that case, the gods likely would have been as helpless to stop her rampage as humans had been before. Her presence would have definitely acted as a major chaotic element in the conflict between the great gods that followed as well.
dictionary.evolution: Hmph! This is pretty handy, for a technique he created! Where shall we head off to annihilate first?
dictionary.fusion: No, this is not enough in the absolute! I've become incomparably beautiful, so you must give me something incomparable, too!
dictionary.summon:
I gained power, haven't I?
So let's tear the world apart!
You're into the idea, right?
